name: Library of Hex
description: 64 unique pairs of collectible sister spellbooks minted to both the Bitcoin and Ethereum blockchains. One for each permutation of Hex’s elemental dimensions (🌀 Flow 💥 Turmoil 💎 Zuànshí) and worldcrafting tools (🔮 Aethereal 🦠 Biocypher 🔱 Nextech). Zed Zeroth, an established British-licensed cryptoasset vendor, is bringing this groundbreaking collection to life by combining traditional pen-and-paper worldbuilding and digital graphic design with cutting-edge AI enhancement and Bitcoin Ordinal inscription technology.
